      л л                                                                л л
      л л On with the update release information:                        л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л Elemental: War of Magic v1.09 Update                           л л
      л л ====================================                           л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л ***************                                                л л
      л л * Multiplayer *                                                л л
      л л ***************                                                л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Added code to prefer a random map that supports the max      л л
      л л   players                                                      л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Cloud saving/loading enabled                                 л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - AI opponents enabled                                         л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Added handling for if firewall is turned off                 л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Added check for if player is disconnected before starting    л л
      л л  turn timer when the end turn is requested                     л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Added check to prevent player from going to multiplayer menu л л
      л л  if it's still checking for an update                          л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л **********************                                         л л
      л л * Gameplay / Balance *                                         л л
      л л **********************                                         л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - AI sovereigns take more care about where they are doing      л л
      л л   their attacking                                              л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Added code so that AIBasic is smarter about attacking units  л л
      л л   in cities                                                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - "Equipment Cache" goodie hut now hands out cloth armor,      л л
      л л   instead of the patchwork armor that should not be in the     л л
      л л   game anymore                                                 л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - You can no longer train groups of Dragons, Catapults, or     л л
      л л   Giant Demons                                                 л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - New option: Players can choose not to have monsters spawn    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - New option: Players can disable minor factions               л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Loot given by monsters increased                             л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug where some AI-controlled caravans that had already л л
      л л   established trade routes would wander off those routes while л л
      л л   delivering their stuff at a city                             л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed a bug where caravan pathfinding through territory      л л
      л л   owned by anyone other than their owner would still have a    л л
      л л   penalty, even through caravans can always move freely        л л
      л л   through any territory                                        л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Changed dynasty kids to determine their essence based on the л л
      л л   BASE essence of their parents (ignoring equipment, player    л л
      л л   ability bonuses, etc.) This should keep kids from double-    л л
      л л   dipping from things like player-wide essence bonuses and     л л
      л л   keep their max mana at more reasonable levels                л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - fixed several armor and special ability xml issues (that     л л
      л л   were either pointed out on the forums or that I discovered   л л
      л л   while fixing others)                                         л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л ***********                                                    л л
      л л * Battles *                                                    л л
      л л ***********                                                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - The starting side in a tactical battle is now chosen         л л
      л л   randomly. The attacker and the defender have an equal chance л л
      л л   to go first.                                                 л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Added shorter/faster annimations for bow attacks and spell   л л
      л л   attacks                                                      л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed a divide by zero error in spell damage.                л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed some logic to determine whether or not a tactical unit л л
      л л   was moving.                                                  л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Added code to make sure a unit cancels its destination when  л л
      л л   it skips a turn.                                             л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Added some additional checks to skip turn logic in tacatical л л
      л л   battles to stop a turn from being skipped in the middle of   л л
      л л   other actions.                                               л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fix to be sure ranged attacks don't always do max damage in  л л
      л л   tactical battles.                                            л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fix to experience display for battles, and fixed a bug where л л
      л л   auto resolve was only rewarding experience for killing the   л л
      л л   leader unit.                                                 л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - The AI does not take its first turn immediately after the    л л
      л л   window loads. This will prevent cases where the AI takes its л л
      л л   turn before the window finishes rendering.                   л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed a spell type tag for Quicken (now shows up in Tactical л л
      л л   Battles)                                                     л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed an issue where a single unit might lose its mana after л л
      л л   attacking and killing a defending team.                      л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Added the UsableInBattle tag for item types, will help to    л л
      л л   determine if an item should be displayed during a tactical   л л
      л л   battle. This defaults to FALSE.                              л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Items in a tactical battle will now properly stack in the    л л
      л л   UI.                                                          л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л ******                                                         л л
      л л * UI *                                                         л л
      л л ******                                                         л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - NEW! City List window which can be brought up via a tab on   л л
      л л   the kingdom screen                                           л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - this will list all your current cities, along with vital     л л
      л л   information about resource, training, and building being     л л
      л л   done there (ie: it's a city spreadsheet)                     л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - New icons hooked up for sovereign talents                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Got rid of trailing decimal zeros for the global resource    л л
      л л   pool tooltips, to clean up the display of resources that are л л
      л л   always integers                                              л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug where the global resources for a player didn't     л л
      л л   refresh when a city was lost through razing until the next   л л
      л л   turn                                                         л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Tweaked the spell info card to get the stats to show up in   л л
      л л   the grey bar at the bottom of the info card, and to support  л л
      л л   multiple text entries of varying sizes                       л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Item Shop now shows change in Combat Speed, Defense, and     л л
      л л   Attack for the highlighted item                              л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Message Box input field now limited to 20 chars              л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Made auto-select next moveable unit code not select caravans л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed City HUDs clipping at the end (now they all get        л л
      л л   rounded edges)                                               л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л ***************************                                    л л
      л л * Performance / Stability *                                    л л
      л л ***************************                                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Moved code around that calls clean-up functions so that we   л л
      л л   don't get false mem-leak messages anymore                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Moved clean up code around so that game within a game cleans л л
      л л   up properly                                                  л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed mem leak in Trigger Manager, city wall nodes,          л л
      л л   destination and selection cursors for destroyed objects      л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Removed code in CTreeGraphic that was causing a leak         л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed big leak in DecalGraphicGraphicManager where every     л л
      л л   decal in the game was leaking when starting a new game       л л
      л л   within a game                                                л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed leak in CUnitSceneViewWindow (which is used on lots of л л
      л л   screens)                                                     л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed random crash in kingdom screen with the filling of the л л
      л л   Lore Book                                                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Tile Designs now flush out the graphics for their "base      л л
      л л   graphic" (the one that the graphic instances use to render)  л л
      л л   once the instances for that base graphic are released        л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed crash if a spellcaster ever had to cancel more than    л л
      л л   one enchantment at a time from losing 2 or more available    л л
      л л   enchantment slots                                            л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed memory leak in UnitAnimationHelper that caused unit    л л
      л л   gfx to leak after the unit was destroyed                     л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed memory leak in TreeGraphic that caused tree batches to л л
      л л   leak on game within a game or destruction of the forest      л л
      л л   object                                                       л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л *************                                                  л л
      л л * Bug Fixes *                                                  л л
      л л *************                                                  л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug where mini map would not update itself after       л л
      л л   starting a new game from within a game                       л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Hooked up renaming cities and units to use events (for MP)   л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug where you could go into the enchants tab for any   л л
      л л   unit and cancel their enchantments, whether that unit        л л
      л л   belonged to you or not                                       л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug where destination cursor would disappear if the    л л
      л л   unit it belonged to was off-screen                           л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Added support for Resource modifier types in unit ability    л л
      л л   bonus options to be taken into account in what resources a   л л
      л л   unit always provides, without needing to be stationed in a   л л
      л л   city                                                         л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed Bug When reload a game with Wild Shard Improvements,   л л
      л л   the game now properly relinks them to their resource hoards  л л
      л л   (fixed issue where destroyed shrines would not regenerate    л л
      л л   shard resource)                                              л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed particle effect render order on main map screen        л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed graphical bug where mounted units in an army did not   л л
      л л   scale properly                                               л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - CalculateAbilities now uses champions for ability modifiers  л л
      л л   (this fixes NPCs that should give bonuses but didn't, such   л л
      л л   as "Royalty")                                                л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug where the NPC AI player would spawn new NPCs based л л
      л л   off of the unit types of dynasty kids. This would cause      л л
      л л   champions wandering around with the same name, and with baby л л
      л л   portraits if they hadn't grown up yet.                       л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Attacking cities or lone improvements while in attack mode   л л
      л л   now works                                                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - hooked up the cursor to change to the crossed swords at the  л л
      л л   right time for cities/improvements when one of your units is л л
      л л   selected                                                     л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed comment in CityLevelUpBonuses.xml that caused          л л
      л л   malformed xml                                                л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed badly merged text in QuestUnits.xml for Talax          л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed end tags in CoreCityWalls                              л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed game modifiers and ending tag after Magnar_Staff in    л л
      л л   CoreSpecialWeapons.xml                                       л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed end tag for Thumb in SpecialUnitProps.xml              л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed comments in UnitSoundPacks.xml                         л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - note: thanks to kenata and heavenfall for helping us     л л
      л л   hunt down those above XML issues down and pointing us to     л л
      л л   some cool data checking tools                                л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л ***********                                                    л л
      л л * Modding *                                                    л л
      л л ***********                                                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Tile Editor: Fixed bug where large silhouette figure would   л л
      л л   render in the middle of a tile design when placing           л л
      л л   pedestrians                                                  л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Map Editor: when using the creature placement tool, defaults л л
      л л   to giving the creature a random wander radius, which can be  л л
      л л   changed with the tool's third spinner in the bottom left     л л
      л л    corner                                                      л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Also changed the wander radius 0 item to say "Don't Wander"  л л
      л л   instead, does what the default used to do, cause the unit to л л
      л л   not even go into auto-patrol mode                            л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Added new data def type, CSpellResourceCost, which can be    л л
      л л   used in spell def xml to specify resource costs on casting a л л
      л л   spell, as well as any persistent maintenance costs if this   л л
      л л   spell is an enchantment                                      л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - tag used in the SpellResourceCost xml object to say whether  л л
      л л   the cost is deducted at time of casting (Per-Turn is 0), or  л л
      л л   if it is a continued maintenance cost that exists as long as л л
      л л   the spell is in effect through an enchantment (Per-Turn is   л л
      л л   non-zero)                                                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Note: maintenance resource costs can only be per-turn if the л л
      л л   spell is an enchantment; there's no one-time cut to per-turn л л
      л л   resource production from an instant, non-enchantment spell   л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Here's an example of some xml to put in a spell def, making  л л
      л л   this spell cost 5 metal immediately when cast, and having a  л л
      л л   maintenance cost of 1 material per turn until the            л л
      л л   enchantment is cancelled:                                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л Metal                                                          л л
      л л 5                                                              л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л Materials                                                      л л
      л л 1                                                              л л
      л л 1                                                              л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - MODs folders now creatured for the user in their My          л л
      л л   Games/Elemental folder                                       л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed Bug: Quests read in from XML (after loading the        л л
      л л   Data.zip) no longer override QuestDefIDs                     л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Images and models now read in from the Mods/GFX folder       л л
      л л   properly                                                     л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Mods are now enabled by default in Prefs.ini                 л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Overlay: Implement tile upload/download                      л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л Elemental: War of Magic v1.08 Hotfix Update                    л л
      л л ===========================================                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л **********************                                         л л
      л л * Gameplay / Balance *                                         л л
      л л **********************                                         л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - New Sovereign Ability: Wealthy +1 gildar per turn            л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - New Sovereign Ability: Green Thumb +2 food per turn          л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Organized Sovereign Ability removed                          л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Shop Costs moved to be a formula (unless specified in the    л л
      л л   XML)                                                         л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Research costs increased                                     л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - More balancing of initial resource seeding                   л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fertile land availability increased                          л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Long Bows now cost 40 gildar to construct                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Default shop values on weapons and armor removed from XML    л л
      л л   (you can overrride the formula still)                        л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Teleport/Blink mana cost increased from 5 to 15.             л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Eliminated criminal adventurers (caused confusion amongst    л л
      л л   players)                                                     л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Pioneer Kit Gold cost reduced from 10 to 5, Materials cost   л л
      л л   increased from 1 to 10.                                      л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Organized ability added to general special abilities         л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Late game monster respawning reduced.                        л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Increased movement speed of units in tactical battles        л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л *************                                                  л л
      л л * Bug Fixes *                                                  л л
      л л *************                                                  л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Added logic to stop spells from dealing max damage every     л л
      л л   time.                                                        л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Restored old terrain/tile movement costs until that can be   л л
      л л   better addressed.                                            л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Adjusted the combat speed from 2 to 3 for the base           л л
      л л   male/female sov units.                                       л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug where Karavox, Magnar, and Verga sovs only had 1.0 л л
      л л   for combat speed.                                            л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug that made it not load any maps except mp maps      л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug resetting default map size to tiny                 л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug where rapidly clicking the fortify action for a    л л
      л л   unit twice or more would cause the game to hang              л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug where, after unhiding the game lobby wnd once,     л л
      л л   human players would get assigned team 1 when joining a       л л
      л л   custom game, instead of an unused team ID                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed crash when restarting new campaign after you load a    л л
      л л   saved campaign game                                          л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug where Cancel button would not show up on           л л
      л л   mutliplayer Join Game with Password screen                   л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed an error where old saves with old data had logic       л л
      л л   conflicts with new code that made spells miss.               л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л Elemental: War of Magic v1.08 Update                           л л
      л л ====================================                           л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л ***************                                                л л
      л л * Performance *                                                л л
      л л ***************                                                л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - LOD optimizations across improvements and tile designs       л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Continued memory optimization/leak squashing                 л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л **********************                                         л л
      л л * Gameplay / Balance *                                         л л
      л л **********************                                         л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - AI handles its sovereign more intelligently                  л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - AI more effective at going after targets of opportunity      л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - AI sovereign is more careful about going into enemy          л л
      л л   territory                                                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - AI has new APIs for determining whether there are targets of л л
      л л   opportunity in the area                                      л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Balance pass on resource distribution                        л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Base tech cost changed from 4 to 5                           л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Merchants/Money Changers now require 1 food to construct     л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Study/Archivist now require 1 gildar per turn to maintain    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Gildar deposit now seeded near starting location             л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Tracker talent cost changed from 15 to 10                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Organized talent cost changed from 10 to 20                  л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Combat Rating calculation altered in an attempt to be a more л л
      л л   accurate gauge of lethalness                                 л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fewer resources spawned per 1000 tiles.                      л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fewer minor factions spawned.                                л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Added scalars to attack and defence for units who are in     л л
      л л   home territory or foreign territory, modifiable in           л л
      л л   ElementalDefs.xml                                            л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Territory scalars now work as Empire v Fallen (e.g. Kingdom  л л
      л л   guy on Fallen territory gets penalty, etc).                  л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Updated formula for gildar given when killing a given unit   л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Child essence is no longer modified by spawn rating, but is  л л
      л л   instead a value between 50% and 100% of the more powerful    л л
      л л   parent's essence.                                            л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Updated TerrainTypes.xml to make Forests and Swamps take 2   л л
      л л   moves                                                        л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Changing the "IncreaseMorale" modifier attribute to -        л л
      л л   AdjustMorale. It's more clear for the modders.               л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л ***********                                                    л л
      л л * Battles *                                                    л л
      л л ***********                                                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Revamp of the way offensive spells hit/miss and deal their   л л
      л л   damage                                                       л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - HIT/MISS is deteremined by an attacker roll (minDamage -     л л
      л л   maxDamage) and by the defender roll (0-DEF)                  л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Values can now be specified as a MinValue and a MaxValue     л л
      л л   rather than just a Value (support for constant value spells  л л
      л л   is still supported)                                          л л
      л л                                                                л л 
      л л - If a MinValue and a MaxValue is specified, the Value is      л л
      л л   defined by a rand roll between the two numbers based on the  л л
      л л   modifiers internal rand roll.                                л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Updated descriptions for all core spellbook spells to show   л л
      л л   bonus damage from INT and bonus damage from shards in the    л л
      л л   spell description.                                           л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - The SpellbookWnd has been updated to properly display the    л л
      л л   damage range if there is one, and the constant damage if     л л
      л л   there isn't one.                                             л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - All core spells that were using stats to calculate the       л л
      л л   value but didn't have a ValueOwner specified have been       л л
      л л   fixed.                                                       л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - The elemental shards unit stats now default to 0 instead of  л л
      л л   1. The calculations in the existing spells have been redone  л л
      л л   to reflect this.                                             л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed BURNING BLADE spell to appropriately increase attack.  л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed SHIELD OF FIRE spell to appropriately increase         л л
      л л   defense.                                                     л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed CRUSH SPIRIT spell to appropriately decrease morale.   л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed BRAVERY spell to appropriately increase morale.        л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed DRAIN LIFE spell to appropriately transfer HP from     л л
      л л   target to caster.                                            л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л ******                                                         л л
      л л * UI *                                                         л л
      л л ******                                                         л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Changed the display code for the main UI bar to round attack л л
      л л   and defense rather than truncate.                            л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Hooked up the CTRL+ARROW and SHIFT-ARROW camera rotation and л л
      л л   movement hotkeys to tactical.                                л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Added save game descriptions                                 л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л *************                                                  л л
      л л * Bug Fixes *                                                  л л
      л л *************                                                  л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug where dialogs from triggers in the campaign (like  л л
      л л   moving beyond where you should build a city) would pop up    л л
      л л   many times when a unit moved into that tile.                 л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed AI bug where it was doing deficit spending and         л л
      л л   creating units still                                         л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Removed the max spell points entry from the affected stats   л л
      л л   in the level up wnd, since it isn't affected by any unit     л л
      л л   stats anymore                                                л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug where non-aggression pact wasn't being checked for л л
      л л   when left-clicking on a unit in attack mode                  л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed modifier in Refined_Economics_Amarian_MP to modify     л л
      л л   A_Gold player ability instead of A_Wealth (which doesn't     л л
      л л   exist)                                                       л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed golem animation pack (commented out an animation that  л л
      л л   was missing and causing t-poses)                             л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed crash when making a mountain in map editor             л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed trading your spouse (if she was a recruited NPC) in    л л
      л л   the regular unit trade                                       л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Perceived value stuff gets hidden when arranging marriages,  л л
      л л   instead of showing whatever was selected last                л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Entries for kids when arranging marriages now use a male and л л
      л л   female icon to denote boy and girl, instead of the words in  л л
      л л   parentheses after the name                                   л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed "..." from string overflowing for the divider title    л л
      л л   when trading or arranging a marriage                         л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed the divider title not ever changing from "And" once    л л
      л л   the arrange marriage screen was shown                        л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed display of tooltip text and color text on Customize    л л
      л л   Faction window                                               л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Tweaked SetToolTip to calculate the necessary size of the    л л
      л л   window more accurately, to fix bug where tooltips were       л л
      л л   sometimes being truncated                                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug where clicking a new destination while the unit    л л
      л л   was moving would cause the unit to get a free move           л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - You can no longer set a units destination while it is moving л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed Refined Housing and Refined Economics techs (and their л л
      л л   fallen equivalents) so that they correctly provide the bonus л л
      л л   they say they do                                             л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - When a unit inside a city or an army is selected and asked   л л
      л л   to cast a spell, that is the unit that is used for           л л
      л л   spellcasting now, instead of having it just fail (in a city) л л
      л л   or try to cast the spell from the leader of the army         л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug where summoning a unit while in a city would cause л л
      л л   that unit to be summoned in an army with you within that     л л
      л л   city (causing weird behavior), now just stations the unit in л л
      л л   the city with you                                            л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug where raise land spell would not work on all land  л л
      л л   category terrain types, like swamp or rugged terrain. Now,   л л
      л л   if a land tile is not hills, it raises that land to hills,   л л
      л л   instead of checking for only some terrain types              л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed a bug where, in the faction editor, you could select   л л
      л л   ability bonus options for free by selecting and deselecting  л л
      л л   them, and then spinning the race spinner, caused by          л л
      л л   deselection not updating the faction config correctly        л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed units that finished training on the same turn as an    л л
      л л   autosave not being there when the autosave was loaded        л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed players not being able to select their city level up   л л
      л л   bonuses or tech breakthroughs on loading an autosave if they л л
      л л   were earned that turn, by having the local player mark       л л
      л л   themselves as needing to get user input for these things     л л
      л л   instead of unhiding the windows to allow the choice right    л л
      л л   away during CWorld::EndTurn, and not letting the user choose л л
      л л   until after the next turn starts and the autosave has been   л л
      л л   made. If one of thses autosaves is loaded, the local player  л л
      л л   will be allowed to choose their tech breakthroughs and city  л л
      л л   bonuses once the map is unhidden. This keeps us from having  л л
      л л   to delay an autosave and the start of the next turn by       л л
      л л   waiting for the user to choose their bonuses, instead making л л
      л л   that choice part of the start turn logic after the autosave  л л
      л л   has been made and saving the mark saying the player will get л л
      л л   to choose at the start of the next turn.                     л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed treaty turn counts not matching if an autosave was     л л
      л л   loaded                                                       л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Based on confusion in the forums, removed ability to         л л
      л л   automatically unlock a spell in the learning queue if it     л л
      л л   makes it to the front of the queue when the player has       л л
      л л   enough research to buy it, so that users rearranging their   л л
      л л   spell learning queue don't have their spell points silently  л л
      л л   taken away while shuffling spells around, if they didn't     л л
      л л   intend to learn that spell next                              л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Now it always takes at least one turn to learn any spell     л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug where tile highlights in tactical battle would     л л
      л л   disappear after an ALT+TAB                                   л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed bug where trees would not look correct in all cases    л л
      л л   after loading a gamesave.                                    л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed an issue that was allowing counter attacks against     л л
      л л   units with abilities of type DoesNotProvokeCounterattacks.   л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed an issue that was causing modifiers applied in         л л
      л л   tactical battles to persist after the battle.                л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - This fixes the bug that causes XP and Gildar rewards after   л л
      л л   battles to be negatively skewed if the enemy unit combat     л л
      л л   rating was lowered due to debuffs.                           л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л л - Fixed an issue with skipping turns in tactical battles that  л л
      л л   would cause a stuck turn if done when the unit being skipped л л
      л л   was in motion. - Pressing spacebar now sets a tactical units л л
      л л   moves to zero AND cancels their destination.                 л л
      л л                                                                л л
      л А                                                                л А
